          p.fs-ms.text-muted.mb-0 It's not a surprise that nowadays over 70% of users shop online using their mobile devices. Cartzilla is 100% responsive and optimized for small touch screens.
        .col-lg-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.mb-grid-gutter.pb-2
          img(src='img/intro/features/07.png' width='90' alt='Google Fonts icon').inline-block.mb-3
