          p.fs-ms.text-muted.mb-0 Cartzilla uses Google fonts which are free, fast to load and of very high quality. Currently Google fonts library includes 870+ font families to choose from.
        .col-lg-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.mb-grid-gutter.pb-2
          img(src='img/intro/features/08.png' width='90' alt='Touch icon').inline-block.mb-3
          h6 Touch-enabled Sliders
          p.fs-ms.text-muted.mb-0 In the era of touch screens it's important to ensure great user experience on handheld devices, especially when it comes to such frequently used interface component as slider.
        .col-lg-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.mb-grid-gutter.pb-2
          img(src='img/intro/features/09.png' width='90' alt='Vector icon').inline-block.mb-3
          h6 Vector Based HD Ready Icons
          p.fs-ms.text-muted.mb-0 Cartzilla is equiped with font-based icon pack to ensure that infographics and interface icons look sharp on any device with any screen resolution and pixel density.
        .col-lg-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.mb-grid-gutter.pb-2
          img(src='img/intro/features/10.png' width='90' alt='HTML5 icon').inline-block.mb-3
