          p.fs-ms.text-muted.mb-0 All HTML files are checked via W3C validator to ensure 100% valid code. As you probably know invalid HTML limits innovation, but Cartzilla is innovative at its core.
        .col-lg-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.mb-grid-gutter.pb-2
          img(src='img/intro/features/11.png' width='90' alt='JavaScript icon').inline-block.mb-3
